Package com.microsoft.azure.management.cdn

Interface CdnEndpoint

All Superinterfaces:
ChildResource<CdnProfile>, ExternalChildResource<CdnEndpoint,CdnProfile>, HasInner<com.microsoft.azure.management.cdn.implementation.EndpointInner>, HasName, HasParent<CdnProfile>, Indexable, Refreshable<CdnEndpoint>
public interface CdnEndpoint extends ExternalChildResource<CdnEndpoint,CdnProfile>, HasInner<com.microsoft.azure.management.cdn.implementation.EndpointInner>
An immutable client-side representation of an Azure CDN endpoint.
